headline: WTW Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: LONDON, Dec. 11, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), a leading global advisory, broking and solutions company, announced that its Board of Directors approved a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.88 per common share for the quarter ended September 30, 2024. The dividend is payable on or about January 15, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on December 31, 2024. About WTW At WTW (NASDAQ: WTW), we provide data-driven, insight-led solutions in the areas of people, risk
